title: BRIEF-WestJet Reports April Load Factor Of 86 Percent
text:
May 8, 2018 / 12:05 PM / Updated 9 minutes ago BRIEF-WestJet Reports April Load Factor Of 86 Percent Reuters Staff
May 8 (Reuters) - WestJet Airlines Ltd: * WESTJET REPORTS APRIL LOAD FACTOR OF 86.0 PER CENT
* WESTJET AIRLINES LTD - APRIL REVENUE PASSENGER MILES (RPMS), OR TRAFFIC, INCREASED 2.8 PER CENT YEAR OVER YEAR
* WESTJET AIRLINES LTD - APRIL REVENUE PASSENGER MILES (RPMS), OR TRAFFIC, INCREASED 2.8 PER CENT YEAR OVER YEAR
* WESTJET AIRLINES - APRIL AVAILABLE SEAT MILES (ASMS), GREW 1.4 PER CENT OVER SAME PERIOD
* WESTJET AIRLINES LTD - APRIL LOAD FACTOR 86 PERCENT, UP 1.2 PERCENTAGE POINTS YEAR OVER YEAR Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
